{"tid":2514614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彩福集團出聲明與譽宴集團割蓆","createTime":"2021-05-03T11:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T12:24:35.000Z","uid":22556,"like":476,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"4111705b793114585b21dde5eb75999e4032c43e","tid":2514614,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZLVBnzbn5UhpQsLBVAqg8EyVp1ZgDhns9bbeCQ8rp8Ku?filename=tqiJqxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqiJqxN.jpg&h=2ee465c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【集團聲明】<br />\n<br />\n現時由何志強先生及何惠雄先生（何氏兄弟）持有的彩福婚宴集團，包括旗下品牌「彩福皇宴」、「彩福喜宴」及「彩薈軒」，與張家豪先生持有的譽宴沒有任何關係。<br />\n<br />\n彩福品牌在2000年由何氏兄弟及張氏兄弟共同創立。早於2009年，雙方由於發展方向存在分歧而決定把集團分拆分家。<br />\n<br />\n何氏保留「彩福」品牌，而張氏則另外創立「譽宴」品牌至今，兩個集團自此獨立運作，互相不存在任何合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n特此聲明<br />\n<br />\n彩福婚宴集團<br />\n2021年5月3日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/117142035003057/posts/4193963773987509/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F117142035003057%2Fposts%2F4193963773987509%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=9e47ac1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/117142035003057/posts/4193963773987509/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"cafccf9bd64d3276524f8a0aa6cf40f2d8bfe370","tid":2514614,"uid":274149,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"4111705b793114585b21dde5eb75999e4032c43e","tid":2514614,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqiJqxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtqiJqxN.jpg&h=2ee465c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【集團聲明】<br />\n<br />\n現時由何志強先生及何惠雄先生（何氏兄弟）持有的彩福婚宴集團，包括旗下品牌「彩福皇宴」、「彩福喜宴」及「彩薈軒」，與張家豪先生持有的譽宴沒有任何關係。<br />\n<br />\n彩福品牌在2000年由何氏兄弟及張氏兄弟共同創立。早於2009年，雙方由於發展方向存在分歧而決定把集團分拆分家。<br />\n<br />\n何氏保留「彩福」品牌，而張氏則另外創立「譽宴」品牌至今，兩個集團自此獨立運作，互相不存在任何合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n特此聲明<br />\n<br />\n彩福婚宴集團<br />\n2021年5月3日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/117142035003057/posts/4193963773987509/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F117142035003057%2Fposts%2F4193963773987509%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=9e47ac1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/117142035003057/posts/4193963773987509/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"被割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d030cca7e1d1dfe0915f700fa50da3bc297fa03","tid":2514614,"uid":13268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1936b22f49d3336d3f04585d9db1ce012b4c9bc2","tid":2514614,"uid":21545,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條友咁搶口 其實係咪有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b00965f06a31faf1ab1bc6013729b70a198ea6","tid":2514614,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"走狗張🐕"},{"pid":"e3527d5f9c0075610afb776c3cee5b7d3b9419b8","tid":2514614,"uid":278431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgm